[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> On March 31, 2024, Berlin springs forward to DST at 2am, so UTC+01:30
[?2004l[?2004h> correctly becomes Berlin 03:30 CEST (UTC+2).
[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> Files Modified:
[?2004l[?2004h> --------------
